high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the end of the counter.
Pick up the bottle of soap off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk towards the tub, turn right to face the counter.
Open the rightmost cabinet door below the counter and put the bottle of soap inside, then close the cabinet.
Walk over to the tub on your right.
Pick up the bottle of soap off of the tub.
Walk back over to the right side of the sink counter.
Open the rightmost lower cabinet door and put the bottle of soap inside, then close the door.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the left of the sink
Grab the bottle of soap off of the counter
Turn right and face the cabinets on the bottom right of the sink
Put the bottle in the right cabinet
Turn right and go to the tub
Grab the bottle of soap next to the tub
Turn around and look at the cabinets on the bottom right of the sink
Put the bottle in the right cabinet
anns.task_desc: Putting two bottles of soap in a cabinet

high_descs: Turn to the right, walk to the sink on the right
Pick up the perfume bottle from the sink
Turn to the right, walk to the cabinet under the sink
Open the cabinet, put the perfume bottle in it
